percent certainty that it is not the time.

02:18:38.235 --> 02:18:40.070
It's not about time.

02:18:40.236 --> 02:18:43.906
It's not the right time.
It's not even a quarter to the right time.

02:18:45.117 --> 02:18:46.785
June.

02:18:48.412 --> 02:18:49.745
How do you know when...?

02:18:49.913 --> 02:18:53.165
